<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align:center;" align="center">
	<span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;"><span>板凳借钱注册本应用用户协议须知</span></span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;"></span>
